data.description: CLOSE TO SCHOOLS!  Come see this charming 2-story home with its original woodwork and hardwood floors.  This home features 3 to 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, a living room, a formal dining room, a dine-in kitchen, and a lovely sun porch with large windows. The second level holds 3 bedrooms, a full bath with a standalone shower, double vanity, a jetted tub, laundry, and walk-in closets. All appliances, window treatments, wooden swing set, and trampoline will stay. The 24’ x 36’ metal garage is large enough for 2 cars and a small shop. Don’t Delay…Call Us Today!
